      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAW LILIBET (6) comes off an average effort last start when seventh at this track over 320m behind Tiggerlong Bingo (19.00) in a NG. Tough to beat if on-song. ELITE DARA (1) produced a moderate effort last time when seventh at Temora over 330m behind Allergy Free (19.56) in a Grade 5. The form out of last race has been strong. Shapes as one to consider. BORACAY BEAUTY (3) doesn't have the best strike-rate. Finished in the minors latest when second (23.14) at this track and may be close to breaking through. Some good form is emerging from her last run. Hard to beat again. TIGGY TOUCH (2) cannot be ruled out.",
